thread.title_full: Culinary Depot reviewed by Jeff Kimma

author: Jeff Kimma
title: Jeff Kimma
text: I needed a bar faucet and found Culinary Depot web price surfing. Not only did they end up being very local, but had quality selections, and were the best price by far. When I contacted them via phone, I spoke with Beth, who was extremely knowledgeable about her products, but was also very helpful in placing my order. Delivery was also immediate. I will use them again!!
